column5: Notes: All national averages are from the data source, except Hispanics which was calculated by authors. Data are not presented for all races.   Note that for employment and education,  Hispanics may be of any race or two or more races, whereas for all other indicators listed, race categories did not include Hispanic.  For health care affordability, values are weighted to reflect population size.  For employment and education, data are pooled across multiple years to increase sample size. .. represents missing values.
